This article includes four 'lists of countries of the world sorted by their
[[gross domestic product]] [[per capita]] at [[nominal value]]s'. This is the
value of all final goods and services produced within a nation in a given year,
converted at market exchange rates to current U.S. dollars, divided by the
average (or mid-year) population for the same year.
categories: Lists of countries by GDP per capita
